videos.description: T.J. Vasher puts Texas Tech on the board early with a 60-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Vasher dashes for the 60-yard TD

videos.description: Will Grier responds with a 31-yard strike to David Sills V for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Sills answers quickly for WVU

videos.description: Nic Shimonek throws it up to Dylan Cantrell for the 6-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Shimonek tosses 2nd TD to put Texas Tech ahead

videos.description: Keke Coutee makes a play in the open field and gets into the end zone from 6 yards out for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Coutee spins off defender for the TD

videos.description: T.J. Vasher pulls down the 53-yard touchdown  in traffic over the West Virginia defender.
videos.headline: Vasher makes catch of the year nominee

videos.description: Texas Tech extends their lead over West Virginia with a 30-yard touchdown run from Tre King.
videos.headline: King breaks away for 30-yard TD run

videos.description: Will Grier finds David Sills V on the fade to the back of the end zone to keep West Virginia in the game.
videos.headline: Sills pulls down TD in back of the end zone

videos.description: Desmon Smith makes a great interception while on the ground for Texas Tech.
videos.headline: Smith picks off pass on his back

videos.description: Ka'Raun White makes a miraculous grab for West Virginia to make it a one-score game.
videos.headline: White climbs the ladder for the TD grab

videos.description: West Virginia takes the lead as Ka'Raun White finds the end zone for the second time.
videos.headline: White pulls down 2nd TD

videos.description: Will Grier finds David Sills V for the third time as West Virginia makes it a two score game.
videos.headline: Grier connects with Sills for 3rd TD
